        <p>After experiencing the marvel of <%= link_to "Ramen Tatsuya", "http://ramen-tatsuya.com/" %> in Austin, I decided to embark on a personal quest to find some good ramen in Houston. Fortunately, after searching a bit I found some pretty good offerings around town. These are in no particular order.</p>
