        <h4>Best Ramen in Cypress?</h4>
        <p>I was lead to <%= link_to "Taiko", "http://www.yelp.com/biz/taiko-houston-2" %> from a Facebook post by an old high school acquaintance. I don't normally venture out to Cypress to find fine dining (we have plenty of that here in town), but I gave it a try and was impressed. Taiko had the feel of the burbs, but the quaint family-run atmosphere was enjoyable. If you're in the area it's definitely worth a try.</p>
