        <h4>Most Customizable</h4>
        <p>Samurai Noodle has several good ramen offerings, but what sets it apart is customization. They offer two different Tonkotsu broths (regular or extra-rich) and five different noodle firmness options ranging from extra-soft to extra-firm. Want noodles that dissolve without chewing? Like noodles tougher than beef jerky? This place is for you. Another thing that's somewhat unique is they allow you to substitute pork shoulder instead of pork belly which is a lot less fatty. They make their noodles in house behind a glass window that's fun to watch (though it's rarely being used when I'm there). Tell them Ken sent you... and they will probably look at you confused-like.</p>
